{"tid":2268753,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"逆風民調再加一！ 智庫「民主研究所」:川普326-212大勝拜登","createTime":"2020-11-03T04:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T05:32:13.000Z","uid":66087,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dc7b5266af80d7b9399a5e7dc5bfa0a9e6666df7","tid":2268753,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/逆風民調再加-智庫-民主研究所-川普326-212大勝拜登-054745501.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E9%80%86%E9%A2%A8%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF%E5%86%8D%E5%8A%A0-%E6%99%BA%E5%BA%AB-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%89%80-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE326-212%E5%A4%A7%E5%8B%9D%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB-054745501.html&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0Eosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=af344f1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/逆風民調再加-智庫-民主研究所-川普326-212大勝拜登-054745501.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國總統大選投票日將至，據統計已有超過8千萬選民提前完成投票，儘管外界普遍認為民主黨候選人拜登最終將勝出，但英國「週日快報」（Sunday Express）日前委託智庫民主研究所(Democracy Institute)所作民調顯示，川普全國支持度為48％，領先拜登的47％，如依此推算，川普可能獲得326張選舉人票，大勝拜登的212票。<br />\n<br />\n英國《週日快報》稍早報導，與民主研究所合作民調，一直跟其他家民調持不同意見，從今年3月起就看好川普會順利連任。民主研究所聲稱，進行民調會針對「可能投票的選民」，而不像其他民調僅針對「已登記選民」，所以嘗試找出川普的隱性支持者。<br />\n<br />\n在佛羅里達、愛荷華、密西根、明尼蘇達、賓州、威斯康辛等6個搖擺州，該民調指川普以49％支持率領先拜登的45％。把這6州的選舉人票分給川普，川普可拿到326張選舉人票。"},{"pid":"d9e3cee788a960132a76a0b34c3e441292bfa351","tid":2268753,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:51:18.000Z","msg":"味0撚 拜登訓係度贏硬"},{"pid":"622392ba1451a89736d77823604b8da1eb5c189a","tid":2268753,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:52:03.000Z","msg":"左膠又催票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5746dfc5bb03052d93b71587ffd480b9902859ff","tid":2268753,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:54:21.000Z","msg":"Mark Taylor: trump 會連任<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2268737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2268737</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ae56beffa4b377fae73cc8d820da190c2ad0292a","tid":2268753,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:55:06.000Z","msg":"民建聯已夠票"},{"pid":"87ef873509981e86a68d6bf1e4ec2a5380d0f2b9","tid":2268753,"uid":125724,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:55:35.000Z","msg":"英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad34236c8d1907adc1f7cba7dde92a58a9cf2636","tid":2268753,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:01:30.000Z","msg":"咪投票啦，留係宿舍屌閪伏冰啦，排隊投票咁嗮時間，係老嘢先會投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ec540d71053a79ab867042e25ace61e495fa8b","tid":2268753,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"622392ba1451a89736d77823604b8da1eb5c189a","tid":2268753,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:52:03.000Z","msg":"左膠又催票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"與民主研究所合作民調，一直跟其他家民調持不同意見，從今年3月起就看好川普會順利連任。"}]}